text: Chitaura elegans is a species of grasshopper found in Indo-Malaysia.Chitaura elegans at orthoptera.speciesfile.org Two subspecies are recognized: * Chitaura elegans diluta Ramme, 1941 * Chitaura elegans elegans Ramme, 1941 == References == Category:Oxyinae Category:Insects described in 1941
